Server Organization
===================

User Homes
-------------------

User homes are allocated at /home.


Web Domains
-------------------

Each domains is allocated at /var/www/vhosts/$DOMAINNAME. Users have a domain folder with links to their domains at /var/www/vhosts.

Doamins are structured as this:

$DOMINPATH/
  +- config/            Apache configuration for this domain.
  +- httpdocs/          Documents that are accesible via http and https.
  +- httpsdocs/         Documents only accesible via https.
  `- subdomains/        Subdomains for this domain.



